train_policy_two_onnx_fgsm_only.py

It is analogous to the existing train_policy_two_onnx_both.py, but it trains only:

no spectral normalization
robustness loss enabled
FGSM enabled
random robustness samples disabled

and writes to:

models/policy_fgsm_only/
  policy.onnx
  policy_two_copy.onnx
  lipschitz.json
  
  
Where to place it?

Put it into each forecast family’s scripts/ directory, for example:

~/Documents/Verify_nn_prod_plan/extended_experiments_202604/Lipschitz_Guided_Training/Verify_nn_prod_plan/models_20260123/nhits_20260123/scripts/

and analogously for nbeats_20260123/scripts/.

How to train FGSM-only
NHITS
cd ~/Documents/Verify_nn_prod_plan/extended_experiments_202604/Lipschitz_Guided_Training/Verify_nn_prod_plan/models_20260123/nhits_20260123

python3 scripts/train_policy_two_onnx_fgsm_only.py \
  --forecast nhits \
  --forecast-workspace ./models/nhits \
  --epochs 250 \
  --output-scale 0.5 \
  --robust-weight 50.0 \
  --pert-radius 1.0 \
  --eps-q 0.1 \
  --seed 0
N-BEATS
cd ~/Documents/Verify_nn_prod_plan/extended_experiments_202604/Lipschitz_Guided_Training/Verify_nn_prod_plan/models_20260123/nbeats_20260123

python3 scripts/train_policy_two_onnx_fgsm_only.py \
  --forecast nbeats \
  --forecast-workspace ./models/nbeats \
  --epochs 250 \
  --output-scale 0.5 \
  --robust-weight 50.0 \
  --pert-radius 1.0 \
  --eps-q 0.1 \
  --seed 0
How to check it with Marabou

Once training finishes, run the same verifier you already use, just pointing it at policy_fgsm_only.

NHITS verifier run
cd ~/Documents/Verify_nn_prod_plan/extended_experiments_202604/Lipschitz_Guided_Training/Verify_nn_prod_plan/models_20260123

python3 -m nhits_20260123.src.verify_robust_marabou \
  --models-dir nhits_20260123/models \
  --model-path nhits_20260123/models/policy_fgsm_only/policy_two_copy.onnx \
  --eps-q 0.2 \
  --epsf-scaled 1.0 \
  --i-max-scaled 1.0 \
  --f-max-scaled 2.0 \
  --timeout 300 \
  --verbose | tee "output_verify_nhits_fgsm_only_$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M%S).txt"
N-BEATS verifier run
cd ~/Documents/Verify_nn_prod_plan/extended_experiments_202604/Lipschitz_Guided_Training/Verify_nn_prod_plan/models_20260123

python3 -m nbeats_20260123.src.verify_robust_marabou \
